what: R Client for CDSS REST API services
title: R Client for CDSS REST API services
text: « CDSS » CDSS API goal cdssr provide functions help R users navigate, explore, make requests CDSS REST API web service. Colorado’s Decision Support Systems (CDSS) water management system created developed Colorado Water Conservation Board (CWCB) Colorado Division Water Resources (DWR). Thank CWCB DWR providing accessible well documented REST API!

title: Request Diversion Records data — get_divrec
text: type character indicating type data request. Either "divrecday", "divrecmonth", "stagevolume". Default "divrecday". wdid character indicating WDID code structure wc_identifier character indicating whether "diversion" "release" returned. Defaults "diversion", used stagevolume requests. start_date character date request data start point YYYY-MM-DD. end_date character date request data end point YYYY-MM-DD. Default set current date function run. api_key character, optional. maximum number requests per day desired, API key can obtained CDSS.
